                    <msContents>
                        <summary>
                            <p>دیوان فضولی</p>
                            <p>The Turkish Díwán of Fuzúlí of Baghdád (d. 963/1555-6 or 970/1562-3). See
                                Hist. of Ottoman Poetry, vol. III, p. 70 foll., Rieu, B.M.T.C., p. 207, and Flügel,
                                Vienna Cat., vol. 1, p. 638. The preface is wanting.</p>
                            <p>Begins:</p>
                            <p>سالك راه حقیقت عشقه ایلر اقتدا قد انبار العشق للعشاق منهاج الهدى</p>
                            <p>Ff. 81 of 16.8 x 11 c. and 17 ll. Dated 20 Şafar, 1218/12 June, 1803.</p>
                        </summary>
